Navigate to project directory: 
cd ~`/Documents/Forecasting/R/projects/AIS Tanker Tracker`

Start in background (logs to file):
nohup Rscript files/background_launcher.R > logs/launcher.log 2>&1 &

nohup Rscript ~/Documents/Forecasting/R/projects/AIS Tanker Tracker/files/background_launcher.R > ~/Documents/Forecasting/R/projects/AIS Tanker Tracker/logs/launcher.log 2>&1 &

Start in foreground (see output directly):
Rscript files/background_launcher.R

Show launcher process:
ps aux | grep background_launcher | grep -v grep

Show all process details:
ps aux | grep -E 'process_[1-3]' | grep -v grep

Process 1:
ps aux | grep process_1 | grep -v grep

Process 2:
ps aux | grep process_2 | grep -v grep

Process 3:
ps aux | grep process_3 | grep -v grep

Stop all:
pkill -f background_launcher
pkill -f "R --no-echo"

Delete old logs:
rm logs/processes/*.log

Show entire launcher log:
cat logs/launcher.log


See R processes: 
pgrep -a R

